<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>{{ project.label }} — FactTrack Report</title>
<style>
  @page { size: Letter; margin: 0.6in 0.55in 0.6in 0.55in; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 10pt;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 22pt; margin: 0 0 4pt 0; color: #0f3057; }
  h2 { font-size: 14pt; margin: 18pt 0 8pt 0; color: #0f3057; border-bottom: 2pt solid #0f3057; padding-bottom: 2pt; }
  h3 { font-size: 11pt; margin: 10pt 0 4pt 0; color: #0f3057; }
  .subtitle { font-size: 10pt; color: #555; margin: 0 0 14pt 0; }
  .meta-table { font-size: 9pt; margin: 8pt 0 16pt 0; }
  .meta-table td { padding: 2pt 12pt 2pt 0; vertical-align: top; }
  .meta-table td:first-child { color: #555; font-weight: 600; }
  .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2pt 8pt; border-radius: 3pt; font-weight: 700; font-size: 9pt; color: white; }
  .badge.green { background: #2e7d32; }
  .badge.yellow { background: #ed6c02; }
  .badge.red { background: #c62828; }
  .severity { padding: 1pt 6pt; border-radius: 2pt; font-weight: 700; font-size: 8pt; color: white; }
  .sev-critical { background: #b71c1c; }
  .sev-high { background: #e65100; }
  .sev-medium { background: #f9a825; color: #222; }
  .sev-low { background: #388e3c; }
  .findings-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 8.5pt; margin: 6pt 0; }
  .findings-table th { background: #0f3057; color: white; padding: 5pt 4pt; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  .findings-table td { padding: 5pt 4pt; border-bottom: 0.5pt solid #ddd; vertical-align: top; }
  .findings-table td.num { text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .impact { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; white-space: nowrap; }
  .summary-box {
    background: #f4f6fa;
    border-left: 4pt solid #0f3057;
    padding: 10pt 14pt;
    margin: 12pt 0;
    font-size: 10pt;
  }
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 8pt;
    margin-top: 14pt;
    border-top: 0.5pt solid #ccc;
    padding-top: 4pt;
  }
  .pagebreak { page-break-after: always; }
  .cover { text-align: center; padding-top: 1.5in; }
  .cover h1 { font-size: 36pt; }
  .cover .brand { font-size: 12pt; color: #888; letter-spacing: 3pt; margin-bottom: 24pt; }
  .cover .badge { font-size: 14pt; padding: 6pt 14pt; }
  .narrative {
    font-size: 10pt;
    background: #fafbfd;
    border: 0.5pt solid #d0d5e0;
    padding: 10pt 14pt;
    margin: 8pt 0;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .narrative em { color: #666; }
  .tract-status { width: 100%; font-size: 9.5pt; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 6pt 0; }
  .tract-status th { background: #f0f3f8; padding: 5pt 6pt; text-align: left; }
  .tract-status td { padding: 5pt 6pt; border-bottom: 0.5pt solid #ddd; }
  .lease-cal { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 8.5pt; margin: 6pt 0; }
  .lease-cal th, .lease-cal td { padding: 4pt 6pt; border: 0.5pt solid #ddd; text-align: center; }
  .lease-cal th { background: #f0f3f8; }
  .lease-cal td.red { background: #ffcdd2; color: #b71c1c; font-weight: 600; }
  .lease-cal td.yellow { background: #fff9c4; color: #6d4c00; font-weight: 600; }
  .lease-cal td.green { background: #c8e6c9; color: #1b5e20; }
  .small { font-size: 8pt; color: #666; }
  table.simple { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 9pt; }
  table.simple th { background: #f0f3f8; padding: 5pt; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  table.simple td { padding: 5pt; border-bottom: 0.5pt solid #ddd; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ─── PAGE 1: COVER ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="cover">
  <div class="brand">F A C T T R A C K</div>
  <h1>{{ project.label }}</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">East Texas Landwork Report — generated {{ generated_at }}</p>
  <table class="meta-table" style="margin: 32pt auto 24pt auto; text-align: left;">
    <tr><td>Project ID</td><td>{{ project.project_id }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>County</td><td>{{ county_name }}, Texas (FIPS {{ county_fips }})</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Tracts in scope</td><td>{{ project.tracts|length }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Active leases reviewed</td><td>{{ project.leases|length }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Wells reviewed</td><td>{{ project.wells|length }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Public records pulled</td><td>{{ data_sources|length }} sources</td></tr>
  </table>
  <p style="margin: 14pt 0 4pt 0;">Project status</p>
  <span class="badge {{ overall_badge_color }}">{{ overall_badge_text }}</span>
  <p class="small" style="margin-top: 60pt; max-width: 5.5in; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    This report aggregates leasehold risk, curative priority, and project execution
    findings from public records and operator filings. All data sourced from public records.
    No proprietary or customer data is included in this analysis.
  </p>
</div>
<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 2: LEASE RISK & CURATIVE PRIORITY (THE MONEY PAGE) ───── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Lease Risk &amp; Curative Priority</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Ranked findings — top {{ findings|length }} of {{ findings|length }} items</p>

<div class="summary-box">
  <strong>{{ summary.headline }}</strong><br>
  {{ summary.body }}
</div>

<table class="findings-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width: 30pt;">#</th>
      <th style="width: 55pt;">Severity</th>
      <th style="width: 90pt;">Type</th>
      <th>Description</th>
      <th style="width: 110pt;">$ Impact</th>
      <th style="width: 90pt;">Assignee</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  {% for f in findings %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ loop.index }}</td>
      <td><span class="severity sev-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity|upper }}</span></td>
      <td>{{ f.rule_id }}</td>
      <td>
        <strong>{{ f.title }}</strong>
        <div class="small">{{ f.description|truncate(280, true) }}</div>
        <div class="small" style="margin-top: 3pt;"><em>{{ f.suggested_action|truncate(200, true) }}</em></div>
      </td>
      <td class="impact">{{ f.impact_display }}</td>
      <td>{{ f.assignee_display }}</td>
    </tr>
  {% endfor %}
  {% if findings|length == 0 %}
    <tr><td colspan="6" style="text-align: center; padding: 20pt;">No curative items detected on this tract group.</td></tr>
  {% endif %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 3: LEASE EXPIRATION CALENDAR ─────────────────────────── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Lease Expiration Calendar — Next 24 Months</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Color-coded by risk level. Pugh-clause and continuous-development obligations flagged in-line.</p>

<table class="lease-cal">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width: 140pt;">Lease (instrument / lessor)</th>
      <th>Primary term end</th>
      <th>Pugh / Retained acreage</th>
      <th>Continuous prod</th>
      <th>Risk</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for row in lease_calendar %}
    <tr>
      <td>
        <strong>{{ row.instrument }}</strong><br>
        <span class="small">{{ row.lessor }}</span>
      </td>
      <td>{{ row.term_end }}</td>
      <td>{{ row.pugh_status }}</td>
      <td>{{ row.continuous_prod }}</td>
      <td class="{{ row.risk_color }}">{{ row.risk_label }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 4: TITLE CHAIN VISUALIZATION ─────────────────────────── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Title Chain — Annotated</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Chronological chain runback with curative items inline.</p>

{% for tract in project.tracts %}
<h3>Tract: {{ tract.label }}</h3>
<table class="simple">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width: 80pt;">Recorded</th>
      <th style="width: 80pt;">Type</th>
      <th>Instrument / Parties</th>
      <th style="width: 60pt;">Notes</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for entry in tract.chain_entries %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ entry.date }}</td>
      <td>{{ entry.kind }}</td>
      <td>
        <strong>{{ entry.instrument }}</strong>
        <div class="small">{{ entry.parties }}</div>
      </td>
      <td>
        {% if entry.curative %}
          <span class="severity sev-{{ entry.curative_severity }}">!</span>
        {% else %}
          ✓
        {% endif %}
      </td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>
{% endfor %}

<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 5: TRACT MAP ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Tract Map</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Wells colored by status. Lease boundaries (where indexed in public records). Curative-hot zones highlighted.</p>

{% if map_image_path %}
<div style="text-align: center; margin: 12pt 0;">
  <img src="{{ map_image_path }}" style="max-width: 6.5in; max-height: 7in; border: 0.5pt solid #ccc;">
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="summary-box">
  <strong>Map rendering:</strong> interactive HTML map available at <code>{{ map_html_path }}</code>.
  Static raster preview not embedded in this build.
</div>
{% endif %}

<table class="simple">
  <thead><tr><th>Well API</th><th>Lease</th><th>Operator</th><th>Status</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for w in project.wells %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ w.api_no }}</td>
      <td>{{ w.lease_name }} #{{ w.well_no }}</td>
      <td>{{ w.operator_name }}</td>
      <td>{{ w.status }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 6: ACQUISITIONS TRACT STATUS ─────────────────────────── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Acquisitions — Tract Status</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Per-tract acquisition readiness; cleared / blocked / critical labels with NRI math.</p>

<table class="tract-status">
  <thead><tr><th>Tract</th><th>Status</th><th>Open curative</th><th>Critical items</th><th>NRI snapshot</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    {% for row in acquisition_status %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ row.label }}</td>
      <td><span class="badge {{ row.badge_color }}">{{ row.badge_text }}</span></td>
      <td>{{ row.open_count }}</td>
      <td>{{ row.critical_count }}</td>
      <td>{{ row.nri_summary }}</td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<h3 style="margin-top: 20pt;">Field narrative</h3>
<div class="narrative">{{ acquisitions_narrative }}</div>

<div class="pagebreak"></div>

<!-- ─── PAGE 7: PROJECT MANAGEMENT BACKLOG ─────────────────────────── -->
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Project Management — Curative Backlog</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Findings restructured as task assignments with priority + deadlines.</p>

<table class="findings-table">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="width: 30pt;">#</th>
      <th style="width: 90pt;">Priority</th>
      <th>Task</th>
      <th style="width: 80pt;">Assignee</th>
      <th style="width: 75pt;">Deadline</th>
      <th style="width: 60pt;">Status</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  {% for f in findings %}
    <tr>
      <td>{{ loop.index }}</td>
      <td><span class="severity sev-{{ f.severity }}">{{ f.severity|upper }}</span></td>
      <td>
        <strong>{{ f.title }}</strong>
        <div class="small">{{ f.suggested_action|truncate(180, true) }}</div>
      </td>
      <td>{{ f.assignee_display }}</td>
      <td>{{ f.deadline_display }}</td>
      <td>{{ f.status|capitalize }}</td>
    </tr>
  {% endfor %}
  </tbody>
</table>

<!-- ─── APPENDIX ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="pagebreak"></div>
<h1 style="margin-top: 0;">Appendix — Methodology &amp; Data Sources</h1>

<h3>Public data sources</h3>
<ul>
  {% for source in data_sources %}
  <li><strong>{{ source.name }}</strong> — {{ source.description }}. Last pulled: {{ source.pulled_at }}.</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h3>Curative detection rules</h3>
<p>This report runs {{ rules_total }} detection rules against the tract group. Each finding includes a
confidence score (0.0–1.0) reflecting data-quality limitations of public records. Findings below 0.5
confidence are flagged for manual review before action.</p>

<h3>Disclosures</h3>
<p>All data sourced from public records. No proprietary or customer data is used in this analysis.
Dollar-impact estimates use a configurable internal price deck; actual values depend on operator
filings, division-order math, and current market conditions. This report is a curative-prioritization
tool — not a substitute for a licensed Texas attorney's title opinion.</p>

<div class="footer">
  FactTrack v{{ facttrack_version }} — {{ generated_at }} — Project {{ project.project_id }}
</div>

</body>
</html>
